                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "aiDIu",
                      "fill": "#8A8278",
                      "content": "Terracotta #C4633A replaces pure orange. Sage green for success states. The palette feels grown, not manufactured — like clay and linen, not plastic and glass.",
