                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ZaFMK",
                      "fill": "#8A8278",
                      "content": "Teak, leather, linen — the palette references natural materials. The background is a shade warmer than Direction 1. Think Eames lounge chair, not Braun radio.",
